structure.unit: ARTICLE XXXIII(S). NORTH CENTRAL URBAN AREA DISTRICT (NCUAD)

law.catch_line: Conflicts with other Chapters and Regulations.

text.section:
Sec. 33-284.99.53. Conflicts with other Chapters and Regulations.
This article shall govern in the event of conflicts with other zoning, subdivision, or landscape regulations of this code, or with the Miami-Dade Department of Public Works Manual of Public Works.
